This file contains a brief description of Knotter releases,
showing when features have been added to the program.

Knotter 0.5.0 (beta) - Current development
--------------------
* Advanced Export Options
* Movable Grid
* User Manual
* Dockable dialogs
* Per-node settings
* New shape algorithm

Knotter 0.4.0 (beta)
--------------------
* Hide/show graph/knot
* Initial error recovery
* Better Flip selection
* Scale/Rotate selection
* Export bitmap
* Configuration
* Save/restore status

Knotter 0.3.0 (beta)
--------------------
* Snap to Grid
* i18n setup
* Pen Style
* Better Mouse Input
* Flip selection

Knotter 0.2.0 (beta)
---------------------
* Zooming
* Copy/Paste

Knotter 0.1.0 (alpha)
---------------------
First public release
* Basic Editing
* Open/Save
* Undo/Redo
* Style
* SVG Export
